name: Corrupted Data II (Binaural)
description:
Dr Malware viruses hacking Chopin's music databases. 
Artificial intelligences passes 45 Chopin's piano pieces through glitch, chiptune, chopping, noise, collage, 8bit, and binaural processes.
Each piece was transformed into midi and then played by a algorithmic synthetizer. 
Polyphony at its finest: collage glitch noisy electro experimentation. 
Binaural music (8d) HEAR with headphones.
